Song Pong / Guitar Pong

   http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h36x5r9eWWg&list=PLsOxTsr9xDj5hTPJQ_-i3GSPZC0VJC778&feature=share
   
Made with Raspberry Pi in mind, hook up a USB microphone and when it hears a clap it starts a game.

It asks you to sing a note.

Then Pong starts. Sing lower than your original note to move the paddle down, and sing up for up.

OMG license

